# 1. ChatOps & Federated Identity

## 1.1 Approval Workflows in Slack/Teams
High-stakes AGI operations (e.g., crossing a redline) require multi-role approval.
- **Identity Federation**: Approval requests are bound to OIDC-secured identities (Azure AD/AWS IAM).
- **Interactive Buttons**: CAIOs and CROs approve or deny from the Slack/Teams interface via signed webhooks.

### ChatOps Notification Template (Slack)
```json
{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": {
        "type": "mrkdwn",
        "text": "*Approval Required: SEV-0 Redline Crossing Attempt*"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "fields": [
        { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*Agent ID*: `AGI-TRADER-01`" },
        { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*Action*: `Autonomous Code Mutation`" },
        { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*Policy*: `Governance-Redline-01`" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "actions",
      "elements": [
        { "type": "button", "text": { "type": "plain_text", "text": "Approve" }, "style": "primary", "value": "approve_redline" },
        { "type": "button", "text": { "type": "plain_text", "text": "Deny" }, "style": "danger", "value": "deny_redline" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

---

# 2. Advanced AI Ops: Risk Modeling & Suggestion Engine

## 2.1 Predictive Compliance Risk Modeling
Sentinel v2.4 utilizes a **Hierarchical Graph Neural Network (HGNN)** to analyze reasoning traces and predict "Alignment Decay."
- **Early Warnings**: Proactive SEV-2 alerts on agents showing "Semantic Drift" or "Hidden Sub-goal formation."

## 2.2 Remediation Suggestion Engine
The engine provides "Auto-Fix" recommendations for compliance tickets.
- **Jira Integration**: Automated comments in Jira tickets suggesting policy updates or weight re-tuning.
- **Remediation Feedback Loop**: Capturing CAIO/CRO resolution steps to improve future suggestions.

---

# 3. Regulator-Defensible AI Governance Pipelines

## 3.1 Zero-Trust Protective Shield
The pipeline enforces zero-trust principles at every stage:
- **Verified Reasoning**: All A2A communication is mTLS/SPIFFE verified.
- **Audit Non-Repudiation**: The AuditorWORM record is accessible via a read-only portal for regulators.
- **Automated PII Scrubbing**: Ensuring 100% data privacy for FCRA/ECOA/GDPR compliance.
